{
  "stem": "12491.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm not sure that this is when I got the number, or whether I got the number after, eventually, I later arrived in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know for sure.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My number was 69,187.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] This-- from August, 1942, till approximately June, 1943, we were all-- all who were assigned to the airport labor camp-- concentration camp, whichever you want-- were doing well.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "By June or July, 1943, the SS arrived, went through the list of people who the airport has employed, and decided who can stay and who will be taken immediately to concentration Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "About 50% of the people were taken away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My brother, I, and most people who I was associated with stayed behind.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We left-- we were still in the-- at the airport, and we were there till December, 1943.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "In December, 1943, they liquidated the airport, the airport facility, and we were all moved to Plaszow concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There I started working again in the fur shop, where they were repairing fur coats for the eastern front soldiers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By truck.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By truck, under guard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I would guess this was-- we drove 10, 12 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And now-- now we were in Plaszow, and we were-- and our uniforms were changed into striped suits, and we were bonafide concentration camp inhabitants-- prisoners.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what happened there-- of course there was, as-- as people maybe do know, every morning there was a count of everybody present.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And every evening was counted by the present, and you were allowed to go back to your living quarters, which was shelves on which people lived-- on shelves.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Again, having contacts with various people in power, I was assigned a third floor shelf at the end.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
